{
  "$comment": "Bucket rules for the oracle-text drift detector (AGENT_BACKLOG #019 / #020). Each entry classifies a 'differ' result by substring presence/absence in the normalized Forge/Scryfall texts. The detector walks the list in order and assigns the first matching label; an unmatched diff falls into 'other'.",
